{"tid":85540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【霧霾升級版】山西臨汾現酸霧 或令人現急性肺水腫","createTime":"2017-01-18T11:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T14:19:35.000Z","uid":22736,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"842f4adea32369e2509d3cdbaefa375ef972dc71","tid":85540,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:42:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170118&amp;guid=56189970&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170118%26guid%3D56189970%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=VvRda%2FphPWYygqpmMXAMCUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=0c7fed3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170118%26guid%3D56189970%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=90ac86b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170118&amp;guid=56189970&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n霧霾已成為內地民眾的日常，但山西臨汾近日霧霾出現「升級版」，當地出現高濃度的二氧化硫濃霧，科學家稱它為「酸霧」，一旦二氧化硫和PM2.5懸浮顆粒物結合，被帶入肺深部，毒性可增加3至4倍，可引起急性肺水腫和死亡。<br />\n<br />\n中科院大氣物理研究所博士後李汀指出，臨汾近日二氧化硫濃度為每立方米1,303微克，是內地最高水平，而且自1月以來濃度一直居高不下，政府多管齊下，仍無法解決積聚的問題。<br />\n<br />\n當二氣化硫、PM2.5在一起，被人類吸入肺部，咽喉深處馬上會被刺激，像火燒一樣，要是張嘴、咳嗽，更會將這些酸霧吸入肺泡，造成傷害。李汀稱，當地的酸霧問題已達「不敢相信」程度，「不知道臨汾到底怎麼了」。<br />\n<br />\n當局深明二氧化硫積聚的問題，可是當地煤炭消耗量卻不斷增加，逾九成都是用來煉焦、發電，可是當地企業的脫硫裝置形同虛設，廢氣直接排放，污染問題一直解決不了。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/18/194237_93df7faa952ee0cd71d089b0178ca87e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F18%2F194237_93df7faa952ee0cd71d089b0178ca87e.jpg&h=f711ce4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50c48c1ef95e0d0b8217ab034a368dce129b5655","tid":85540,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已不是問題"},{"pid":"c0a0189699b494629c584bf7653371f880b75431","tid":85540,"uid":4874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:46:20.000Z","msg":"鄰國既事 關我撚事"},{"pid":"7106353864a11343177d52b757da7997d5e21ff7","tid":85540,"uid":20035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmemArtYv4PRd7xWWc7B3CMM7LJBvEU4rSLvCNeUaFgCtV?filename=472NM33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F472NM33.jpg&h=96582aeb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aafbaa686bf7c133c1592ad617e80f16f06bd6cd","tid":85540,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鄰國既事 關我撚事</blockquote>天真"},{"pid":"1e5f613364d6c1674f7518d6bde1f7a15b826d65","tid":85540,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:36:26.000Z","msg":"嗰個地方好似係特別癡線<br />\n人均壽命四十幾50"},{"pid":"ee93e60167f24149fed6f13d9669da63a7d6c590","tid":85540,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鄰國既事 關我撚事</blockquote><br />\n到時送大禮俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3a0690d01561f0e5d02a4e2032044c9089ae32","tid":85540,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鄰國既事 關我撚事</blockquote><br />\n睇支那豚仆街死係幾開心架"},{"pid":"21225b195f0c631f613d6584410b6baba138c35f","tid":85540,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:03:45.000Z","msg":"已升級為生化武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77bd12a9fc9fa72645fbc528682aece16a5de775","tid":85540,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:08:31.000Z","msg":"除左恭喜，